import { Box, Card, CardContent, Typography } from "@mui/material";



export const Product = () => {

    return (
        <>
           <Box>

                    <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                                Shoes
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                                NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>

                    <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                                Sun Glass
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                                NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>

                    <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                                Bag
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                                NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>

                    <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>
                        <CardContent>
                            <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
                                Earing
                            </Typography>
                            <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                                NUMBERS RAKHNI HOOO
                            </Typography>
                        </CardContent>
                    </Card>
                </Box>
        </>

    )
};
